{{other people|Mumtaz Begum}}
{{more citations needed|date=February 2016}}

{{infobox person
|name=Mumtaz Begum
|birth_name=Kalyani Ray Chowdhury
|birth_date={{birth date|1923|5|20}}
|birth_place=[[Howrah]], Kolkata, [[Bengal Presidency]], [[British India]]
